          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The isomeric  ratios  in  the  photonuclear  reactions",
                " (gamma,p) at the energies in region of the giant",
                " dipole resonance were measured. The isotopes 98Mo,",
                " 100Ru, 118Sn, and 122Sn  were  irradiated  by  the",
                " bremsstrahlung of microtron.  The  activation  method",
                " was  used  for  measurements of reaction yields.  The",
                " obtained data were compared to  the  results  of  the",
                " statistical model calculations."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CRITIQUE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "It was pointed out (text and table  3)  that  isomeric",
                " ratio  for  isotope 105Rh ground (t-1/2 = 35.4 h) and",
                " isomeric (t-1/2 = 45 s) states was investigated using",
                " the  reaction  105Ru(gamma,p)105Rh (100Ru is mentioned",
                " as target nucleus in abstract!). Both are impossible:",
                " the target must be 106Pd (subent M0616003)."
              ]
            }
          ],
